<HEADLINE> Chinese President Meets Russian Foreign Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALMA ATA, July 3 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin met
Russian Foreign Minister Yevgeny Primakov here Friday.
</P>
<P>
Jiang and Primakov exchanged views on further development of
Sino-Russian relations on the sideline of a meeting of China,
Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Russia and Tajikistan.
</P>
<P>
Primakov was entrusted as the special representative of Russian
President Boris Yeltsin to the five-nation meeting.
</P>
<P>
Kazak President Nursultan A. Nazarbayev, Kyrgyz President Askar
A. Akayev and Tajik President Emomali S. Rakhmono attended the
meeting. 
