entry of Palestinian workers into its territories if the European
Union (EU) boycotted products from the occupied lands. He said the
EU had adopted decisions seeking good cooperation with the
Palestinian authority and Israel and an improvement of the
Palestinians' economic situation was in the interest of Israel
itself. 
