<HEADLINE> Netherlands, Argentina 1-1 at Halftime </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
MARSEILLE, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The Netherlands and Argentina
played to a 1-1 draw at halftime in a quarter-final match at the
World Cup finals here on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Patrick Kluivert put the Netherlands 1-0 ahead at the 12th
minute when he got a perfect pass from fellow striker Dennis
Bergkamp and beat the Argentine goal-keeper with an easy shot.
</P>
<P>
The Argentine team fought back to level the score at 1-1 eight
minutes later when Claudio Lopez beat a Dutch off-side trap for the
equaliser. 
