<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, July 4 (Xinhua) -- From 12 to 15 million people in
France watched the quarter-final game between the French national
football team and its Italian counterpart on Friday, a record
high number of watchers since the World Cup finals began.
</P>
<P>
