<HEADLINE> Cafu to Miss Semi-final Due to Bookings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
NANTES, July 4 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian defender Cafu will miss the
semi-final match against either Argentina or the Netherlands due to
bookings.
</P>
<P>
Cafu got a yellow card in the quarter-final match against
Denmark. Earlier in the round of 16 match against Chile, he had
already received one.
</P>
<P>
According to the FIFA rules, Cafu will be banned for one match
and that means he will not be available in Brazil's semi-final
match.
</P>
<P>
Cafu felt it was unfair that the Scottish referee gave him the
card:"I didn't deserve a yellow card. I've never got one in such
circumstances before." he said.
</P>
<P>
Yet he was satisfied with the victory over Denmark:"We deserved
it. We made more chances and it would have been quite wrong if we
had not made it through to the semi-finals." 
</P>
</TEXT>
